    h3 Summary of Experience
    .content Jay Fallon is a User Experience professional with many years of experience in web-based, user-centric product design and development, employed as both a consultant and full-time team member on over thirty projects for a list of clients that include large enterprises, small businesses and start-up ventures. Jay's interests lie in perfecting information architecture, social communication and usability.
  
