    .position User Experience Developer
    .date July 2000 – December 2007
    .content Duties include providing technical expertise to account managers, user experience and development teams as well as executing the user experience requirements into deliverables for integration with web applications or standalone websites. Client list includes Fidelity Management & Resource Company, State Street Global Advisors, Johnson & Johnson, Pfizer and ADQSR.
    
